Data Types in X++
Int -- Integer Values
Real -- Decimal values
str -- string
boolean -- true/false
date -- date values
utcdatetime -- date&time
container -- collection of mixed values 

examples 

int total = 10;
str name = "Ram";
boolean flag = true;
real Amount = 10.5;
date currentDate = 09-01-2026;
utcdatetime today = 09-01-2026 14:37:35;

in this way we declare the datattypes.
